fields.title: AMD Threadripper 3990x
fields.description:
64 Cores & 128 Threads
Base Clock: 2.9GHz, Max Boost Clock: up to 4.3GHz, 288MB Cache, TDP: 280W
System Memory Specification: 3200MHz, System Memory Type: DDR4, Memory Channels: 4
Socket: sTRX4, Motherboard Compatibility: AMD TRX40 chipset based motherboards
Graphics: Separate Graphics Card is required, Heatsink Fan: Not included in the box, Warranty: 3 Years
